OL,7,FAs one of 153 signatories to the
OL,8,FGenocide Convention, South Africa is
OL,9,Fentitled to file such a case with the
OL,10,FICJ.
OL,12,FThe convention, which was ratified on
OL,13,FDecember 9, 1948, represented the
OL,14,Finternational community's commitment
OL,15,Fto "never again" repeat the atrocities
OL,16,Fcommitted by Nazi Germany during the
OL,17,FSecond World War.
